OceanESIP

   Ocean ESIP is a member of NASA's Earth Science Information Partner
   (ESIP) Federation. Ocean ESIP provides improved satellite data products
   and simulation model output in support of global change studies of the
   oceans.
   _______________________________________________________________________



   Sea Surface Height Residual (example):

   sea_surface_height_img_small

Global Ocean Data

   Data available on this site:
     * Sea level from the TOPEX/Poseidon altimeter
     * Sea Surface Temperature (NCEP/Reynolds)
     * Wind and wind stress from the NSCAT, ERS-1 and ERS-2 scatterometers
     * Barotropic Model along the TOPEX/Poseidon groundtrack (New)
   _______________________________________________________________________

   Data accessible through:
     * Graphical User Interface
     * Digital Earth (Web Mapping Testbed)

